  "field": "accounting",
  "role": "method",
  "bullets": [
   "Japanese timely disclosure PDFs filed through the Tokyo Stock Exchange TDnet system, spanning eight disclosure types, each paired with a document-type-specific JSON schema.",
   "Three GPT-5.4 variants, full, mini and nano, run zero-shot schema-guided structured extraction under four reasoning-effort settings, three times each, scored against schema core fields.",
   "GPT-5.4 with high reasoning effort scored highest at 0.905 core-field accuracy; best settings varied by document type and higher reasoning effort did not consistently improve accuracy."
  ],
  "bullet_provenance": "ai",
